title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 707 - The Framed Great Detectiv
description:
[LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan - 707 - The Framed Great Detective [English Sub]

A previous case comes to haunt Kogorou and the rest of the police. The public eye misconstrues Kogorou's intentions as suspicion, and his image is in tatters after an altercation in a department store. It's up to Conan, Takagi and Chiba to clear Kogorou's name and finally bring justice to a killer.
